Package mloss.roc

Provides the core classes of Roc used for ROC/PR analysis.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Curve
    This class is a binary classification result analysis suitable for producing ROC and PR curves.
    Curve.Builder<TScore extends java.lang.Comparable<? super TScore>,TLabel>
    Builds Curve objects in multiple, flexible ways.
    Curve.PrimitivesBuilder
    This class is the same as Curve.Builder except this takes arrays of primitives as input (instead of sequences of objects).

Package mloss.roc Description

Provides the core classes of Roc used for ROC/PR analysis.

  • Curve is the main class for ROC/PR analysis.
  • The builders (Curve.Builder and Curve.PrimitivesBuilder) provide convenient ways to construct Curve.
